Package ca.griis.ontorelquery.exception

Class OntoRelQueryException

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Throwable
java.lang.Exception
ca.griis.ontorelquery.exception.OntoRelQueryException
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConfigurationException, GraphException, QueryException, UserFriendlyException
public abstract class OntoRelQueryException extends Exception
Base abstract exception class for the OntoRelQuery project. This class serves as the parent for all specific exception types in the project.

Object Properties

  • Unicity: yes (uniqueness of each exception instance).
  • Clonability: no (exceptions should not be cloned).
  • Modifiability: no (exceptions are immutable once thrown).
